<h1 id="choosing-a-software-process">Choosing a Software Process</h1>

<ul>
  <li>
    <h2 id="organizational-factors">Organizational factors</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Is the team co-located or global?</li>
      <li>How is the team structured(Are thre PMs? Small teams? Large Team?)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h2 id="technology-factors">Technology factors</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>How does the team like to work? Whiteboard or online tracking?</li>
      <li>Do you have access to software to manage communication effectively?</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h2 id="domainsector-factors">Domain/Sector factors</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>how quick is the turnaround on a products?</li>
      <li>Are there constant updates?</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h2 id="regulatory-factors">Regulatory factors</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Are you building something that requires government or other third-party oversight?</li>
      <li>What docs / artifiacts will you have to provide?</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h3 id="agile-methodologies">Agile Methodologies</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Scrum</li>
      <li>Extreme Programming(XP)</li>
      <li>Kanban</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <h3 id="plan-driven-methodologies">Plan-Driven Methodologies</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Rational Unified Process(RUP)</li>
      <li>Personal Software Process(PSP)</li>
      <li>Team Software Process(TSP)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

